Package: CausalGRN
Type: Package
Title: CausalGRN: Deciphering Causal Gene Regulatory Networks from Single-Cell CRISPR Screens
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Bo", "Yu",
      email = "byu2@fredhutch.org",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    ),
    person(
      "Wei", "Sun",
      email = "wsun@fredhutch.org",
      role = c("aut", "cph")
    )
  )
Description: A scalable computational framework to infer causal Gene Regulatory
    Networks (GRNs) from single-cell CRISPR screens. CausalGRN mitigates
    spurious correlations in sparse scRNA-seq data and orients the network
    using perturbation outcomes to predict cellular responses to unseen
    perturbations.
